sub_title: Commercial Manager | S&V | NL | Metal parts | Welded frames | Engineering
summary:
I am both technical and commercial minded. I like to push my boundaries and work with an international team. My current job introduces me to multiple disciplines. In addition, I am involved in strategic business processes related to Rubitech Alucast.

Disciplines:
- Sales and Business development
- Project Management
- Engineering and Design
- Logistics and Procurement.

The following qualities suit my personality to a greater or lesser extent:
- Creative and Result-oriented
- Effective and Win-Win
- Commercial and Technical

When I was 20, I moved to Malaysia for a six-month internship. In that time I learned a lot about international business and how to embrace different cultures. Besides my work I enjoy cycling, cooking or making music.
